Package: ClinKit
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Hualin", "Wang", , "wanghualin@stu.njmu.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive, opinionated toolkit for routine clinical analyses. Provides one-click functions for univariate/multivariable logistic or multinomial regression, restricted cubic splines, quartile-based analyses, ROC curves, forest plots, interaction testing, baseline tables, and publication-ready figures. All outputs (tables, figures, Word reports) are generated automatically with sensible defaults and minimal boilerplate code.
